channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: JD Vance Responds to Walz's Debate Challenge, Nukes Kamala's 'Vibe' Campaign
Trump says 'new category' of crime under Biden-Harris administration is 'beyond control'
item.description: Former President Trump told an Asheville, North Carolina, crowd on Wednesday that the Biden-Harris administration is responsible for a new crime that is "beyond control" called "migrant crime."

item.title: YouGov Poll: Inflation, Economy, Immigration Top Issues
item.description: Inflation, the economy and immigration are the top three most important issues facing Americans heading into the 2024 presidential race, according to new survey released Wednesday by The Economist/YouGov.

item.title: Surprise! Nation's Capital Ranked As Least Desirable Place to Live in the Entire US of A
Harris dodging flip-flop attacks as faceless surrogates flip on key positions: 'Playing politics'
item.description: Campaign officials for Vice President Harris have been the ones to announce her new stance on key issues she opposed during her 2019 presidential campaign.

item.title: Billy Graham's Son Rips 'Evangelicals for Harris' Ad
item.description: The son of late evangelist Billy Graham is hitting back after a group calling itself "Evangelicals for Harris" used a clip of his father in a campaign ad targeting Evangelical Christians in battleground states.

item.title: Elon Musk Trolls the Left With Video of Him and Trump

item.description: A new report by an American energy advocacy group is warning about a legal training program that it says is â€œcorruptly influencing the courts and destroying the rule of law."

item.title: Caroline Sunshine to Newsmax: Trump Fights for American Prosperity
item.description: Contrasting Donald Trump and Vice President Kamala Harris, Caroline Sunshine, deputy communications director for the Trump campaign, told Newsmax on Wednesday that the former president is fighting to make America prosperous again and that Harris is out for herself.

item.title: Columbia University President Resigns Amid Constant Anti-Semitic Campus Controversies
Senate Dem in key battleground race flip-flopped on student debt under Biden: No 'magic wand'
item.description: Longtime Senate Democrat Bob Casey has flip-flopped on student debt forgiveness, with unearthed video showing he did not support debt forgiveness in 2014.

item.title: Kids Online Safety Act Stalls in the House
item.description: The Kids Online Safety Act has hit resistance in the House of Representatives suggesting the highly anticipated bipartisan legislation may not pass without modifications.
